# The format of this file is identical to `.dockerignore`.
# It is used to reduce the size of deployed images to make the process of publishing faster.

# Private runtime, agent, and workspace state must never enter a published image.
**/.git
**/.agents
**/.claude
**/.codex
**/.codex-watch*
**/.codex-log-watch
**/.pyrus-runtime
**/.local
**/.cache
**/.config
**/.gstack
**/.pythonlibs
**/.venv
**/.vendor
**/.mypy_cache
**/.pytest_cache
**/.ruff_cache

# Dependencies and generated output are rebuilt for publication.
**/node_modules
**/target
**/dist
**/coverage
**/tmp
**/output
**/reports
**/.headless-shots
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
**/attached_assets

# Audit tooling and agent handoffs are not application runtime inputs.
security/pentest
**/SESSION_HANDOFF_*.md
**/CODEX_HANDOFF_*.md
**/CLAUDE_HANDOFF_*.md
**/AGENT_CHAT*.md
**/AGENT_CHAT*.jsonl
**/AGENTS.md
**/CLAUDE.md

# Secrets and private-key containers are denied by name and type.
**/.[eE][nN][vV]
**/.[eE][nN][vV].*
!.env.example
**/*.[pP][eE][mM]
**/*.[kK][eE][yY]
**/*.[pP]12
**/*.[pP][fF][xX]
**/*.[jJ][kK][sS]
**/*.[kK][eE][yY][sS][tT][oO][rR][eE]
**/*.cpuprofile
